im-fury-bikini-model-claimed-Pakistans-entry.html |title=Muslim fury after bikini model claimed to be Pakistan's entry &#124; Mail Online |work=Daily Mail  |location=London |date= September 7, 2006|accessdate=October 26, 2010 }}</ref> third runner-up in the [[Miss Pakistan World]] pageant<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mariyahamoten.com/bio.php |title=The Official Mariyah A. Moten \u2013 Mariyah Bio |publisher=Mariyahamoten.com |accessdate=October 26, 2010 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100302103657/http://www.mariyahamoten.com/bio.php |archivedate=March 2, 2010 }}</ref>\n*[[Misbah Yasin- Iqbal|Misbah Iqbal]] \u2013 Mrs. Pakistan World 2007/2008; from Houston, Texas\n*[[Natasha Paracha]] \u2013 born in [[Islamabad, Pakistan]]; now living in [[New York City]]; Pakistan's 6th [[Miss Pakistan World]], in 2008<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.pakspectator.com/profile-and-pictures-of-natasha-paracha/ |title=Profile and Pictures of Natasha Paracha &#124; The Pakistani Spectator |publisher=Pakspectator.com |date=June 16, 2008 |accessdate=October 26, 2010 |archive-url=http://webarchive.loc.gov/all/20110709113028/http://www.pakspectator.com/profile-and-pictures-of-natasha-paracha/ |archive-date=July 9, 2011 |url-status=dead |df=mdy-all }}</ref>\n*[[Ramina Ashfaque]] \u2013 [[Miss Pakistan World]] 2016\u20132017; from [[Miami]], [[Florida]]\n*[[Shanzay Hayat]] \u2013 Shanzay Hayat,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://newseastwest.com/miss-pakistan-shanzay-hayat-does-it-again/|title=Miss Pakistan Shanzay Hayat does it again!|accessdate=December 14, 2015}}</ref> from [[Waziristan]], [[Pakistan]] now living in [[New York City]], became Pakistan's 11th [[Miss Pakistan World]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.silobreaker.com/shanzay-hayat-wins-miss-pakistan-world-in-mississauga-5_2267075717424480283|title=Silobreaker|accessdate=December 14, 2015|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130904062222/http://news.silobreaker.com/shanzay-hayat-wins-miss-pakistan-world-in-missi