surgeon)|Muhammad Ali Shah]] (orthopaedic surgeon)\n* [[Ziauddin Ahmed]] (Ziauddin Chain of Hospitals, [[Ziauddin Medical University|Ziauddin Medical]] University\n==Militants==\n*[[Ghazi Baba]], mastermind of 2001 Delhi parliament attack\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Muhajir people| ]]\n", "name_user": "DeltaQuad", "label": "safe", "comment": "Removing link(s):Wikipedia:Articles for deletion/Hammad Siddiqiclosed as soft delete (XFDcloser)", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Muhajir_people"}
