fe]] \u2013 journalist<ref>{{cite book |title=Taking Back Islam: American Muslims Reclaim Their Faith: Books: Producers of Beliefnet, Michael Wolfe |date= 2004-08-16|isbn = 978-1579549886|last1 = Wolfe|first1 = Michael}}</ref>\n* [[Fareed Zakaria]] \u2013 author, commentator, and host of [[CNN]]'s ''[[Fareed Zakaria GPS]]''<ref>Seema Sirohi (2003-04-28) [http://www.dailytimes.com.pk/default.asp?page=story_28-4-2003_pg4_8 Will Fareed Zakaria be the first Muslim US secretary of state?] Daily Times. Retrieved on 2009-06-16.</ref>\n*[[Khaled Hosseini]] \u2013 [[Novelist]], [[physician]]<ref>{{cite news|publisher=Dawat Independent Media Center (DIMC) |title=A Critical Response to the Pashtun Bashing in The Kite Runner, by Nationalist Pashtun Rahmat Rabi Zirakyar |url=http://www.dawatfreemedia.org/english/index.php?mod=article&cat=pashto&article=134 |url-status=dead |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140815201352/http://www.dawatfreemedia.org/english/index.php?mod=article&cat=pashto&article=134 |archivedate=August 15, 2014 }}</ref>\n*[[Melody Moezzi]] \u2013 author and activist<ref>{{cite news|publisher=Penguin Random House|title = Melody Moezzi's Author Page|url=http://www.penguinrandomhouse.com/authors/240759/melody-moezzi}}</ref>\n*[[Wael Abdelgawad]] \u2013 author\n\n==See also==\n*[[Glossary of Islamic terms in Arabic]]\n*[[List of converts to Islam]]\n*[[List of Islamic and Muslim related topics]]\n*[[Lists of Muslims]]\n*[[Lists of people by belief]]\n*[[Taqwacore]]\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist|25em}}\n\n{{Expand list|date=June 2009}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:American Muslims}}\n[[Category:Lists of Muslims]]\n[[Category:American Muslims| ]]\n[[Category:Lists of American people]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikipedia list article}}\n{{pp|small=yes}}\n{{use mdy dates|date=December 2015}}\nThis is an incomplete list of [[Notability in the English Wikipedia|notable]] Muslims who live or lived in the United States.\n\n==Academia==\n[[File:Adil Najam in 2010.JPG|