ns Up About The Roles He Won't Play And What's Missing In Hollywood|url=https://www.huffingtonpost.com/2015/04/08/muslims-in-entertainment_n_7007410.html|publisher=HuffPost|date=April 8, 2015|accessdate=July 11, 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Modeling==\n[[File:Iman Abdulmajid.jpg|thumb|upright|Supermodel [[Iman (model)|Iman]]]]\n*[[Halima Aden]] \u2013 Somali-American fashion model<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.allure.com/story/halima-aden-cover-story-july-2017|title=Muslim Model Halima Aden on Defying Beauty Standards|publisher=Allure|date=July 2017|accessdate=20 June 2017}}</ref>\n*[[Iman (model)|Iman]] \u2013 [[supermodel]] and wife of [[David Bowie]]<ref>[https://www.bbc.co.uk/worldservice/learningenglish/webcast/tae_betterspeaking_archive.shtml Talk About English] BBC. Retrieved on 2009-06-18.</ref>\n*[[Bella Hadid]] \u2013 [[Model (person)|fashion model]] and daughter of real-estate developer [[Mohamed Hadid]] and former model [[Yolanda Hadid]]<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.arabnews.com/node/1078966/fashion|title=I am proud to be a Muslim|date=April 4, 2017|work=ELLE|access-date=April 4, 2017|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Young|first1=Sarah J.|title=Bella Hadid: \"I am proud to be a Muslim\"|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/bella-hadid-muslim-islam-faith-father-refugee-us-sisters-paestinian-jordanian-american-a7665611.html|website=The Independent|accessdate=4 April 2017|language=English|date=4 April 2017}}</ref>\n\n==Music==\n[[File:IceCube Toronto2006.jpg|thumb|upright|Rapper [[Ice Cube]] performing in 2006]]\n*[[Ahmad Jamal]] \u2013 [[jazz]] [[pianist]]<ref>''On the Side of My People: A Religious Life of Malcolm X''. Louis A. DeCaro, Jr. (1997). p. 147</ref>\n*[[Ahmet Ertegun|Ahmet Erteg\u00fcn]] \u2013 Songwriter and founder of [[Atlantic Records]]<ref>Turkish Coalition of America, [http://www.tc-america.org/tribute_071507.html \"Congressional Tribute to Ahmet Ertegun\"], May 24, 2007</ref>\n*[[Akon]] \u2013 R&B and hip-hop artist<ref>Fr