an]] wrestler in [[World Wrestling Entertainment|WWE]]\n*[[Mustafa Ali (wrestler)|Adeel Alam]] \u2013 [[Pakistani American]], wrestler in [[World Wrestling Entertainment|WWE]]\n*[[The Iron Sheik|Khosrow Vaziri]] \u2013 Retired [[Iranian American]] wrestler, former [[WWE Championship|WWE Champion]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://bidoun.org/articles/twilight-of-the-iron-sheik|title=Twilight of the Iron Sheik: A wrestler in winter|author=Negar Azimi|work=[[Bidoun]]|date=2008|accessdate=February 20, 2019}}</ref>\n\n===Mixed martial arts===\n*[[Muhammed Lawal]] \u2013 former Strikeforce Light Heavyweight World Champion\n*[[Kamaru Usman]] \u2013 current UFC Welterweight Champion\n\n==Television==\n[[File:Dr Oz (cropped).png|thumb|upright|[[Mehmet Oz]] at the 2010 ''Time'' 100 Gala]]\n* [[Mara Brock Akil]] \u2013 screenwriter, producer<ref>{{cite web|title=Mara Brock Akil|url=http://www.beliefnet.com/Faiths/Islam/2009/09/Muslim-Celebrities.aspx?p=5|work=Muslim Celebrities|publisher=Beliefnet|accessdate=September 3, 2011}}</ref>\n* [[Usman Ally]] \u2013 actor<ref>{{cite news|title=Usman Ally On His 'Veep' Role As a Turning Point for Muslims on TV|url=http://www.awardsdaily.com/2017/06/23/usman-ally-interview/|publisher=Awardsdaily|date=2017-06-23|accessdate=2017-06-27}}</ref>\n*[[Ahmed Shihab-Eldin]] \u2013 reporter for national news channels<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.muslimpublicservice.org/node/90|title=Virtual Globetrotter - The Life and Times of Ahmed Shihab-Eldin|publisher=Muslim Public Service Network|accessdate=July 31, 2017|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160914161901/http://muslimpublicservice.org/node/90|archive-date=September 14, 2016|url-status=dead}}</ref>\n* [[Rizwan Manji]] \u2013 actor<ref>{{cite news |title=Outsourced's Rizwan Manji: 'It's a great honour' |url=https://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/arts/television/outsourceds-rizwan-manji-its-a-great-honour/article1743925/ |publisher=The Globe and Mail | location=Toronto |date=2012-08-23}}</ref>\n*[