aza Khan]]\n*[[Siddiq Ismail]]\n*[[Khursheed Ahmad]]\n\n=== Video jockeys ===\n* [[Anoushey Ashraf]]\n* [[Ayesha Omar]]\n* [[Mahira Khan]]\n\n==Sports==\n\n===Squash===\n*[[Jansher Khan]], 8 time world open champion, 4 time super series champion, 6 time British champion\n*[[Aamir Atlas Khan]]\n*[[Farhan Mehboob]]\n*[[Hashim Khan]], 8 time British champion\n*[[Jahangir Khan]], 6 time world champion, 10 time British champion\n*[[Carla Khan]]\n*[[Mansoor Zaman]]\n*[[Qamar Zaman]], British champion\n\n===Athletics===\n*[[John Permal]], sprinter\n\n===Boxing===\n*[[Muhammad Waseem]], WBC Silver Flyweight Champion\n\n===Cricket===\n*[[Imran Khan]]\n*[[Anil Dalpat]]\n*[[Imam-ul-Haq]]\n*[[Salman Butt]]\n*[[Asif Ali (cricketer, born 1989)]]\n*[[Asif Ali (cricketer, born 1991)]]\n*[[Shaheen Shah Afridi|Shaheen Afridi]]\n*[[Nasir Jamshed]]\n*[[Javed Miandad]]\n*[[Abdul Hafeez Kardar]]\n*[[Mohammad Hafeez]]\n*[[Abdul Qadir (cricketer)|Abdul Qadir]]\n*[[Abdul Razzaq (cricketer)|Abdul Razzaq]]\n*[[Aamer Sohail]]\n*[[Danish Kaneria]]\n*[[Fazal Mahmood]]\n*[[Faisal Iqbal]]\n*[[Fawad Alam]]\n*[[Hanif Mohammad]]\n*[[Iftikhar-ul-Haq]]\n*[[Imran Abbas (cricketer)|Imran Abbas]]\n*[[Imran Nazir (cricketer)|Imran Nazir]]\n*[[Inzamam-ul-Haq]]\n*[[Javed Burki]]\n*[[Junaid Khan (cricketer)|Junaid Khan]]\n*[[Kamran Akmal]]\n*[[Khan Mohammad]]\n*[[Majid Khan (cricketer, born 1946)|Majid Khan]]\n*[[Misbah-ul-Haq]]\n*[[Mohammad Amir]]\n*[[Mohammad Asif (cricketer)|Mohammad Asif]]\n*[[Mohammad Umar Taj]]\n*[[Mohammad Yousuf (cricketer, born 1974)|Mohammad Yousuf]] \n*[[Moin Khan]]\n*[[Mushtaq Ahmed (cricketer)|Mushtaq Ahmed]]\n*[[Rashid Latif]]\n*[[Saeed Ajmal]]\n*[[Saeed Anwar]]\n*[[Saqlain Mushtaq]]\n*[[Sarfraz Ahmed]]\n*[[Sarfraz Nawaz]]\n*[[Sajjida Shah]] \n*[[Shahid Afridi]]\n*[[Sohail Tanvir]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://content-uk.cricinfo.com/pakistan/content/player/43265.html|title=Sohail Tanvir|publisher=}}</ref>\n*[[Shahid Khan Afridi]]\n*[[Shoaib Akhtar]]\n*[[Shoaib Malik]]\n*[[Umar Akmal]]\n*[[Umar Gul]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://english.ohmynews.com/articleview/article_view.asp?at_code=392527&no=345551&rel_no=1|title=Cricket: Pakistan Faces a Host of Problems \u2013 OhmyNews International|publisher=}}</ref>\n*[[Waqar Younis]]\n*[[Wasim Akram]]\n*[[Yasir Hameed]]\n*[[Yasir Shah]]\n*[[Younis Khan]]\n*[[Zaheer Abbas]]\n* [[Zahid Ahmed (Pakistani cricketer)|Zahid Ahmed (cricketer)]]\n*[[Zahid Fazal]]\n*[[Babar Azam]]\n*[[Fakhar Zaman (cricketer)|Fakhar Zaman]]\n\n=== E-sports ===\n* [[Suma1L|Syed Sumail Hassan]]\n\n===Field hockey===\n*[[Hassan Sardar]]\n*[[Samiullah Khan (field hockey)|Samiullah]]\n*[[Shahbaz Ahmad]]\n*[[Shahid Ali Khan]]\n*[[Sohail Abbas]]\n*[[Tahir Zaman]]\n*[[Samiullah Khan (field hockey)|Samiullah Khan]]\n*[[Basit Ali]]\n*[[Mohammad Zahid (cricketer, born 1976)|Mohammad Zahid]]\n*[[Shahnaz Sheikh]]\n*[[Islahuddin]]\n*[[Jack Britto]]\n*[[Imran Mayo]]\n\n===Golf===\n* [[Taimur Hussain]]\n\n===Sailing===\n*[[Munir Sadiq]]\n\n===Snooker===\n*[[Khurram Hussain Agha]]\n*[[Mohammed Yousuf (snooker player)|Mohammed Yousuf]]\n*[[Naveen Perwani]]\n*[[Saleh Mohammad (snooker player)|Saleh Mohammed]]\n*[[Muhammad Asif (snooker player)|Muhammad Asif]]\n\n===Tennis===\n* [[Aisam-ul-Haq Qureshi]]\n* [[Haroon Rahim]]\n\n===Football===\n*Lt Col. (R) [[Younus Changezi]], former member of national football team\n*[[Muhammad Essa]], striker of the national football team\n*[[Kaleemullah Khan (footballer)|Kaleemullah Khan]], striker of the national football team; currently playing [[Sacramento Republic FC]]\n*[[Jaffar Khan]], legendary goalkeeper\n\n===Mountaineers===\n*[[Ashraf Aman]]\n*[[Nazir Sabir]]\n*[[Hassan Sadpara]]\n*[[Samina Baig]]\n*[[Amir Mehdi]]\n\n===Skiing===\n* [[Amina Wali]]\n\n===Mixed martial arts===\n* [[Bashir Ahmad (mixed martial artist)|Bashir Ahmad]]\n\n==Police officers==\n*[[Chaudhry Aslam Khan]]\n*[[Malik Saad]]\n*[[Allah Dino Khawaja]]\n*[[Nasir Durrani]]\n*[[Moazzam Jah Ansari]]\n==Militants==\n*[[Abdul Rauf Azhar]]\n*[[